Creation of EFT file is computerized. It is done by accesssing databases and running server side code.
The data will be stored in the Choc An Data Center as per the requirements. 
Some of the hardware required will be the terminal card reader, 
servers to connect and store the data as well as modems and routers to connect to the internet. 
The system will have to work with a banking system to manage financial records. 
It will also work with a delivery system to manage imports and exports. 
Users will swipe their cards and get immediate feedback from the terminal.